OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774576986
OL,3,CTwo arrested on suspicion of funding
OL,4,Cterrorism
OL,6,FTwo people have been arrested in
OL,7,FOxford on suspicion of funding
OL,8,Fterrorism.
OL,10,FCounter Terrorism Policing South East
OL,11,F(CTPSE) said a 50-year-old man and a
OL,12,F35-year-old woman remain in custody
OL,13,Ffollowing the arrests on Thursday. (26
OL,14,FMarch)
OL,16,FCTPSE are being supported by Thames
OL,17,FValley Police as they carry out
OL,18,Fsearches at an address in the city,
OL,19,Fthe force said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
