OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774576986
OL,3,CTwo arrested on suspicion of funding
OL,4,Cterrorism
OL,6,FAn increased police presence is
OL,7,Fexpected in the Cowley area while
OL,8,Fsearches take place.
OL,10,FThe suspects have been arrested on
OL,11,Fsuspicion of arranging funds for the
OL,12,Fpurpose of terrorism, contrary to
OL,13,Fsection 17 of the Terrorism Act 2000,
OL,14,Fpolice said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
