CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774576986
OL,3,CTwo arrested on suspicion of funding
OL,4,Cterrorism
OL,6,FSuperintendent Jen Hogben, of Thames
OL,7,FValley Police, said: "Arrests of this
OL,8,Fnature can cause some in the community
OL,9,Fto feel concerned, however they form
OL,10,Fpart of a pre-planned operation led by
OL,11,Four colleagues in Counter Terrorism
OL,12,FPolicing South East and there is no
OL,13,Fimmediate risk to the public.
OL,15,F"We will continue to offer support to
OL,16,FCTPSE while their investigation
OL,17,Fcontinues.
